<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="manner-n">manner <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /'mænə(r)/    美 /'mænər/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1">1.★ <strong>方式；方法</strong></h4>
<p>the way that sth is done or happens：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>My father disapproves of my <strong>manner of</strong> living.
我父亲不赞同我的生活方式。</p></div>

<h4 id="2">2.★ <strong>举止；态度</strong></h4>
<p>the way that sb behaves towards other people：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>His manner was polite but cool. 
他举止彬彬有礼但显冷淡。</p></div>

<h4 id="3">3.★ <strong>礼貌；礼仪</strong></h4>
<p>polite ways of behaving in social situations：</p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>table manners</strong> 
餐桌礼仪</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p><strong>It’s bad manners to</strong> stare at people.
盯着别人看不礼貌。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>In any case, a lot can be accomplished by a smile and <strong>good manners</strong>. 
在任何情况下，微笑和有礼貌都会让你有很大收获。</p><footer>2011 安徽</footer></div>

<h2 id="_2">固定搭配</h2>
<h3 id="all-manner-of">all manner of</h3>
<p>1.<strong>[正式用语] 各种各样的：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>The problem can be solved in all manner of ways. 
这个问题可以用多种方式解决。</p></div>

<h3 id="in-a-manner">in a ... manner</h3>
<p>1.<strong>用…的方式 / 态度：</strong>  </p>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>They worked in an orderly manner. 
他们有条不紊地工作。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>She greeted me in a friendly manner. 
她友好地和我打招呼。</p></div></div>